==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unreliable
<hw>Un`re*li"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not reliable;
untrustworthy. See <er>Reliable</er>.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Un`re*li"a*ble*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Alcibiades . . . was too unsteady, and (according to Mr.
Coleridge's coinage) ⟦ldquo⟧<qex>unreliable</qex>;⟦rdquo⟧ or perhaps, in
more correct English, too ⟦ldquo⟧unrelyuponable.⟦rdquo⟧</q> <rj><qau>De
Quincey.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unreligious</ent>⟦br⟧
